title: Confirmed: The Expendables 4 will arrive in 2017
text:
Confirmed: The Expendables 4 will arrive in 2017 
Published By: TotalFilm.com - Today 
Sylvester Stallone is getting the band back together once more, with The Expendables 4 set to hit cinemas in 2017
